snippet.title: Godstone - Early Access Trailer | 2025
snippet.description:
The time has finally come! 8 years in development, this is a massive passion project I have worked on solo - and at last the early access is near!

Thank you so much to everyone who has supported me along the way - let's make the final stretch.

Wishlist Godstone on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1715030/Godstone/

Support my work on Ko-Fi:
https://ko-fi.com/dementedplant
